No. 112,

October Term, 1952.

Sobell v. United States. Frank J. Donner, Arthur Kinoy, Marshall Perlin and Benjamin Dreyfus for petitioner. Solicitor General Rankin for the United States.

The motion to vacate the orders denying petitions for writ of certiorari, 344 U. S. 838, and rehearing, 344 U. S. 889, and the request for oral hearing on motion are denied.
